data.description: This spacious 2 bedroom, 2 full bathroom residence is located in the highly desirable, gated, secure Trio complex. The open floor plan illuminates abundant natural light. The kitchen has an island and all stainless steel appliances. The living room includes a fireplace & a door to the balcony. The primary bedroom has 2 closets and a full bathroom en-suite. Huge attached 2 car tandem garage plus additional parking right in front. Territorial view. Community club house w/ pool, spa, workout room, wifi, big screen & pool table. Close to shopping, restaurants, and entertainment. Home owner in process of removal/declutter. Motivated seller. Come See all that this property has to offer at this price!
